    "Title": "Orange Level Contract: Destroy Outlaw Infrastructure",
    "Description": "An opportunity has presented itself for a client to take action against a group of criminals who have been harassing their business.\n\nAccording to reports, this group of outlaws are currently laying low at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>. The client thinks this is a good time to catch them off guard and bring them to justice. The job is to take out their fuel tanks and putting an end to their smuggling operations once and for all.\n\nThese folks are not to be underestimated. You better bring some backup and fly low to avoid the turrets. Priority as always is the fuel tanks.\n\nGood luck,\n\nKevin Walton\nDispatcher, Foxwell Enforcement\n'Security, Your Way'\n\nFoxwell Enforcement is a bonded security specialist licensed to operate throughout the UEE. We are always looking for new operators to join our family. If you or anyone you know is interested, please reach out to one of our contract representatives.",
